content: Īsumā - kartētājs nodzēsa landuse=residential piem. https://osmcha.org/changesets/135951886 un salika visur landuse=grass dzēšot sīkākus gabalus piem. https://osmcha.org/changesets/135935355 vai https://osmcha.org/changesets/135933705 Tas viss ar komentāru "Update". Te principā laikam vajag visu to revert. Man uz doto brīdi slinkums rakstīt garus changeset komentārus (domāju sākumā īsi, bet ilgāk skatoties, tur daudz problēmu un taisīt visam revertu arī uzreiz krietni lielāks uzdevums). Ļoti entuziastiski un daudz kartē bet te jau drusciņ pa traku. Iepriekš piemēram bija tie nepareizie/nepabeigtie road route un visādi sīkumi.

Tie landuse=grass izskatās dikti nepareizi.
Vai paspēji revertot?
Es neko neesmu darījis, nē. Man slinkums bija visu izskatīt un pārbaudīt. Tur vēl pa virsu daudz cita.

Tu kaut ko rakstīsi? Īss komentārs tur jau atstāts https://www.openstreetmap.org/changeset/135935355 bet te vēl izdzēstie residential un iepriekšējā zāle

Changeset: 135935355 | OpenStreetMap
OpenStreetMap is a map of the world, created by people like you and free to use under an open license.

Nav vēl sanācis - varbūt @UrSuS kā Ventspili agrāk daudz zīmējis ir kaut ko skatījies?
Vai @Dmitry tur ir komentējis, vai es jaucu lietotājus? :)
To jau jebkurš var, vienkārši man absolūti slinkums tagad tik gari ar to nodarboties. Varbūt vēlāk.

I deleted all the incorrectly drawn grass, but did not restore the living areas. I didn't notice that he removed them. https://www.openstreetmap.org/changeset/136168550
https://www.openstreetmap.org/changeset/136168684
Can I talk here in English? Or it will be better if I will translate everything into Latvian?

Changeset: 136168684 | OpenStreetMap
OpenStreetMap is a map of the world, created by people like you and free to use under an open license.
I think most people here can speak English
He also deleted some previous smaller accurate grass areas, which we probably want to restore. But it's all both spread and combined in several changesets, so it's a bit of a pain to undo

Dmitry said:

...
Can I talk here in English? Or it will be better if I will translate everything into Latvian?

Yeah, sure - we welcome (and have here) people from different backgrounds and countries.
If you do speak Latvian, no matter the level, that would be preferred (using local language is one of OSM global semi-rules), but lacking that is not a blocker :)

HellMap said:

He also deleted some previous smaller accurate grass areas, which we probably want to restore. But it's all both spread and combined in several changesets, so it's a bit of a pain to undo

Visus changesetus nevarēja revertot?

Nedaudz "smieklīgi", ka liekot lielos zāles laukums izdzēsa pats savus iepriekš liktos mazākus laukumus. Es tos pa vienam nerevertošu. Bet residential'us gan revertoju https://www.openstreetmap.org/changeset/136183374
